Types

Int128 = object
  when system.cpuEndian == littleEndian:
      lo*: uint64
      hi*: int64

  else:
      hi*: int64
      lo*: uint64
Source   Edit   
SomeInt128 = Int128 | UInt128
Source   Edit   
UInt128 = object
  when system.cpuEndian == littleEndian:
      lo*, hi*: uint64

  else:
      hi*, lo*: uint64
